# Spring Boot 如何启动Tomcat

## 启动日志反推

```json
o.s.b.w.embedded.tomcat.TomcatWebServer  : Tomcat initialized with port(s): 8080
```

- org.apache.catalina.startup.Tomcat#start
- org.springframework.boot.web.embedded.tomcat.TomcatWebServer#initialize
- org.springframework.boot.web.embedded.tomcat.TomcatWebServer#TomcatWebServer(org.apache.catalina.startup.Tomcat, boolean)
- org.springframework.boot.web.embedded.tomcat.TomcatWebServer#TomcatWebServer(org.apache.catalina.startup.Tomcat)
- org.springframework.boot.web.embedded.tomcat.TomcatServletWebServerFactory#getTomcatWebServer
- org.springframework.boot.web.embedded.tomcat.TomcatServletWebServerFactory#getWebServer
- org.springframework.boot.web.servlet.context.ServletWebServerApplicationContext#createWebServer
- org.springframework.boot.web.servlet.context.ServletWebServerApplicationContext#onRefresh
  - GenericWebApplicationContext

## ApplicationContext初始化流程

- org.springframework.boot.WebApplicationType#deduceFromClasspath
- org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication#createApplicationContext
  - `AnnotationConfigServletWebServerApplicationContext`
- org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication#refreshContext
- org.springframework.boot.SpringApplication#refresh
- org.springframework.boot.web.servlet.context.ServletWebServerApplicationContext#refresh
- org.springframework.context.support.AbstractApplicationContext#refresh
- org.springframework.boot.web.servlet.context.ServletWebServerApplicationContext#onRefresh

 

